    <lb n="1"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" extent="2" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/><unclear reason="undefined">πρ</unclear>ος<gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" extent="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" extent="15" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/> ἀνελθεῖν καὶ <choice><corr>ποδοφιλῆσαι</corr><sic>ποδοφειλησαι</sic></choice> <supplied reason="lost">τὸν δεσπότην μου</supplied> 

    <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost"> ἵνα ἐπιτύχω</supplied> τοῦ ἐσπουδασμένου διότι ἐξ ἁμαρτιῶν <choice><corr>ἐρρώσθη</corr><sic>ερρωστη</sic></choice>, καὶ μέχρι τῆς γρα<supplied reason="lost">φῆς</supplied> 

    <lb n="3"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost"> ἐὰν ἀναλάβω ἐ</supplied>μαυτόν, ἀνέρχομαι εἰς πόδας ὑμῶν, ἐπειδὴ κατὰ πολλοὺς τοὺς τρόπους θ<supplied reason="lost">έ</supplied>λω εὑρε<supplied reason="lost">θῆναι εἰς προσκύνησιν ὑμῶν</supplied> 

